@startuml
skin rose
title Email Confirmation Flow
actor User
participant "Email Client" as Email
participant "Next.js App" as Client
participant "Auth Callback API" as Callback
participant "Supabase Auth" as Auth

User -> Email: Click confirmation link
activate Email
Email -> Client: GET /api/auth/callback?code=...
activate Client
Client -> Callback: Handle callback request
activate Callback
Callback -> Auth: exchangeCodeForSession(code)
activate Auth
Auth --> Callback: Valid session tokens
deactivate Auth
Callback -> Callback: Set auth cookies
Callback --> Client: Redirect to next=/
deactivate Callback
Client --> User: Display authenticated app
deactivate Client
deactivate Email

note over User: User is now verified and logged in
@enduml